  ++  ta-emil
    ::    emit move list
    ::
    ::  adds multiple moves to the core's list.
    ::  flops to emulate ++ta-emit.
    ::
    |=  mol/(list move)
    %_(+> moves (welp (flop mol) moves))
  ::
  ++  ta-emit
    ::  adds a move to the core's list.
    ::
    |=  mov/move
    %_(+> moves [mov moves])
