        sh-prod(active.she aud.gam)
      ::
      ++  deli
        ::  gets absolute message number from relative.
        ::
        |=  {max/@ud nul/@u fin/@ud}
        ^-  @ud
        =+  dog=|-(?:(=(0 fin) 1 (mul 10 $(fin (div fin 10)))))
        =.  dog  (mul dog (pow 10 nul))
        =-  ?:((lte - max) - (sub - dog))
        (add fin (sub max (mod max dog)))
